title: Impeachment of Man
description: The acclaimed Aryanist and keeper of the Hitler flame (her book, The Lightning and the Sun, inspired such postwar Hitlerites as George Lincoln Rockwell) argues passionately for a society that transcends the human-centered to recognize the value of all living things. Vegetarian, anti-vivisectionist, and opposed to Jewish ritual slaughter, Impeachment of Man will infuriate, inspire, and inform across the ideological spectrum. Makes a great gift for the young person who thinks that concern for animal rights is "left-wing" and began with PETA
